Ing '''''Chelonoidis nigra abingdoni''''', a awsan da mu namang '''Abingdon Island tortoise''',<ref>[http://www.iucnredlist.org/apps/redlist/details/9017/0 Chelonoidis nigra ssp. abingdoni] [[IUCN Redlist]]</ref> '''Abingdon Island giant tortoise''', '''Pinta giant tortoise'''<ref>{{cite journal | url = http://www.iucn-tftsg.org/wp-content/uploads/file/Accounts/crm_5_000_checklist_v4_2011.pdf | title = Turtles of the world, 2011 update: Annotated checklist of taxonomy, synonymy, distribution and conservation status |journal=Chelonian Research Monographs|volume=5| accessdate =|date=2011-12-31 | author=Rhodin, Anders G.J.; van Dijk, Peter Paul; Inverson, John B.; Shaffer, H. Bradley; Roger, Bour |page=000.xx| archiveurl = http://www.webcitation.org/64t6NrOyR | archivedate = 2012-01-22}}</ref> ampong '''Pinta Island tortoise'''{{cn}}  metung yang [[subspecies]] ning [[paung Galápagos]] a katutubu king [[Ecuador]] a malyaring mewala na.<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Chelonoidis nigra (Geochelone nigra)|publisher=[[IUCN Red List]]|url=http://www.iucnredlist.org/apps/redlist/details/9011/0|accessdate=2012-01-11}}</ref> Ing tawling balu rang indibidwal ning subspecies lalaki yang awsan dang '''Lonesome George'''<ref name="planetark">{{cite web|title=Lonesome George faces own Galapagos tortoise curse|first=Simon|last=Gardner|url=http://www.planetark.com/dailynewsstory.cfm/newsid/9708/newsDate/06-Feb-2001/story.htm|archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20110604055952/http://www.planetark.com/dailynewsstory.cfm/newsid/9708/newsDate/06-Feb-2001/story.htm|archivedate=2011-06-04|date=6 February 2001|accessdate=2012-01-11}}</ref> ({{lang-es|El Solitario Jorge/George}}),<ref name="death_official">{{cite web|title=El mundo pierde al solitario George|author=Proceso de Relaciones Públicas de la Dirección del Parque Nacional Galápagos|url=http://www.galapagospark.org/boletin.php?noticia=628|date=24 June 2012|accessdate=2012-06-25}}</ref> who died on 24 June 2012.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/articleshowpics/14387262.cms|title=Lonesome George, last-of-his-kind Galapagos tortoise, dies| date=25 June 2012}}</ref><ref name="death_official"/><ref>{{cite web|last=Raferty|first=Isolde|title=Lonesome George, last-of-its-kind Galapagos tortoise, dies|url=http://worldnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/06/24/12386484-lonesome-george-last-of-its-kind-galapagos-tortoise-dies?lite|publisher=MSNBC.com|accessdate=2012-06-24}}</ref> Anyang tawli nang banwa, balu re antimong pekamalagad a lelangan king yatu. Migsilbi yang masikan a sagisag i George ning pamagpursigi king pamanyagip king Galápagos ampo king mabilug a yatu.<ref>{{Cite book|last=Nicholls|first=Henry|year=2006|title=Lonesome George: The Life and Loves of a Conservation Icon|publisher=Macmillan Science|location=London|url=http://www.henrynicholls.com/lonesomegeorge.html|isbn=1-4039-4576-4|accessdate=2012-01-11|postscript=<!--None-->}}</ref>

Mumuna yang meyakit i George king isla ning Pinta anyang 1 Deciembre 1971 kapamilatan ning Hungarian a [[malacologist]] a i József Vágvölgyi. Mengasira la reng tanaman ning isla uling kareng mengabulus a kambing a melyap, at metung ne mu ing mitagan king katutubung  ''C. n. abingdoni''. Isipan dang pekilagyu de king tauan a legeng ning artistang [[Estados Unidos|American]]ung i [[George Gobel]]. Miyalis ya para king kaligtasan king [[Charles Darwin Research Station]], i George, a kilung dang kayabe da reng bábaing ibat king aliwang subspecies. Lipat ning menebun la reti, alang miyapsa. Miyatulan yang [[functional extinction|functionally extinct]] o mituring a mewala na ing paû uling makakuling ya i George. Anyang 24 Junio 2012, mete ya i Lonesome George uling king e malinong sangkan.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sns-rt-ecuador-tortoise-tv-pixl2e8ho4g7-20120624,0,4558768.story |agency=Reuters |date=June 24, 2012 |work=Chicago Tribune |title=Lonesome George, last-of-his-kind Galapagos tortoise, dies}}</ref><ref name="joy"/> Paniwalan dang maygit neng dinalan (100) a banwa, at maki timbang yang 200 lbs. Mapalyaring king kayang pangamate, laganas neng mewala o megisan ing kayang subspecies.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.galapagosdigital.com/journal/2012/6/24/lonesome-george-rip.html |title=Lonesome George RIP! |date=June 24, 2012 |first=Cecilia |last=Alvear |work=Galápagos Digital}}</ref> Ing sangkan ning kayalan kasiguradwan, mapalyaring atin pang metung o adwang kayabe king  subspecies a mabibyeng makakulung king isla o king aliwang isla ning Galápagos.

